This focused workshop provides 4 hours of high-quality video training on advanced iPhone and iOS 5 App development presented by expert iOS developer Robert Turrall. Robert will guide you through the more advanced iOS Application Development topics including multithreading and performance issues, adding Twitter Integration to Applications. Other recent additions to the CocoaTouch Framework for iOS5 will also be covered.
